item.title: Attention SBI customers! SBI Utsav special fixed deposit (FD) scheme ends in two days, Check details
item.description: Attention SBI customers! SBI Utsav special fixed deposit (FD) scheme ends in two days, Check details The State Bank of India (SBI) started a limited period offer term deposit called ‘Utsav Deposit’ starting 15 August.
